Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
I think it is a very good chance for students to make friends with others. At the same time, it is also an approach for them to get a feeling of social life. When I was a undergraduate student, I really enjoyed my life living on campu dorm. I made a lot of good friends during that time.